external_knowledge:
- "storms brewing" refers to the occurrence of allegations;
- "ports" symbolizes the incident location;
- "to calm down" or "to find its peace" metaphorically represents the resolution process of incidents;
- The average time to resolution is a measure of law enforcement efficiency.

sql:
SELECT AVG(ctzn_age) AS average_complainant_age
FROM incidents
WHERE allegation = 1;

SELECT incident_date, finding
FROM incidents
ORDER BY incident_date DESC;
